* GF180MCU-D scaffold-only class-F harmonic-tuned RF PA.
* Pins: gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias
* Status: topology seed only; harmonic terminations are placeholders.
.subckt {{netlist_name}} gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias

* Output device.
MMOUT drain gate gnda gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ M1_L }}u w={{ M1_W }}u m={{ M1_M }}

* Input coupling and bias.
CINBLK rfin gate_in {{ Cin_value }}
RGSTOP gate_in gate {{ Rg_value }}
RBIAS gate vbias {{ Rbias_value }}

* Fundamental feed and output coupling seed.
LRFC vdda drain 250n
RRFC vdda drain 10k
COUT drain rfout {{ Cout_value }}
ROUTLEAK rfout gnda 1G

* Placeholder harmonic terminations around 2f0 and 3f0.
R2TERM drain h2_l 8
L2TERM h2_l h2_c 50.7n
C2TERM h2_c gnda 2p
R3TERM drain h3_l 10
L3TERM h3_l h3_c 45.0n
C3TERM h3_c gnda 1p

.ends {{netlist_name}}
